Text: I'd better not get close to those cubes...

Name: Ayla
Text: And that robot guard... seems to communicate with the terminal in certain ways...

Name: Ayla
Text: In short, I have to activate it!

Name: Ayla
Text: Activated the robot guard!

Name: Ayla
Text: Yeah, it works!

Name: Ayla
Text: It seems the Heteromers here could be easily deconstructed...

Name: Ayla
Text: Maybe they've lost too much energy because of Gray Raven.

Name: Ayla
Text: Let me see if the terminal still works.

Name: Ayla
Text: It is activated. Finally I can contact Gray Ravens.

Name: Luna
Text: Lucia, are they...

Name: Lucia
Text: Corrupted, a bit stronger than the ones you saw before.

Name: Lucia
Text: Luna, stay close.

Name: Luna
Text: Roger...

Name: Lucia
Text: Ha... Ha...

Name: Luna
Text: You've been fighting with them all this time...?

Name: Lucia
Text: Luna, try to focus. There's still a...

Name: Luna
Text: But you're already...

Name: Lucia
Text: Luna!

Name: Lucia
Text: Just wait for me...

Name: Lucia
Text: Don't do... anything stupid...

Name: Lucia
Text: I'll be right there... Just wait for me!

Name: The Other Lucia
Text: You seem to have already realized the abnormality...

Name: The Other Lucia
Text: Talk to "me" again... If you are determined to confront it.

Name: Lucia
Text: Yes.

Name: The Other Lucia
Text: As you wish...

Name: Lucia
Text: Luna... I'm sorry...

Name: Mother
Text: You can't go out like that all covered in dust. What will the recruiter say?

Name: Mother
Text: Go put that dress on, sort yourself out in front of the mirror, then come back out.

Name: Liv
Text: Not here... Probably in the closet.

Name: Liv
Text: Such a pretty dress...

Name: Liv
Text: Can I really just wear it...?

Name: Nanami
Text: Must... fight... then... find Mommy and Jane...

Name: Nanami
Text: I did it... but I'm drained...

Name: Nanami
Text: The Corrupted are attacking humans!

Name: Nanami
Text: Wait, why do the Corrupted and humans... all look the same... to me?

Name: Nanami
Text: No... Nanami... Pull yourself together! Look closer...

Name: Nanami
Text: There are two Corrupted!

Name: Guard A
Text: She's coming this way! She's been Corrupted!

Name: Nanami
Text: No, you're...

Name: Guard B
Text: Aim!

Name: Nanami
Text: No... Nanami needs to... get out of here...

Name: Lee
Text: Let's fix this quickly and go home.

Name: Lee
Text: Murray's birthday is coming up. Before that, maybe I can...

Name: Lee
Text: I can send the whole message using 0s and 1s.

Name: Lee
Text: Binary operations, being and nothingness, black and white, order without chaos.

Name: Lee
Text: Prepare to meet your maker. It will be sequential and instantaneous.

Name: Lee
Text: ...The final chip. Murray, your brother I might... have to wish you Happy Birthday ahead of time.

Name: Karenina
Text: Hope today's harvest is good.

Name: Karenina
Text: (Searches and digs around)

Name: Karenina
Text: Nothing at all... Ah! Those people, again!

Name: Karenina
Text: It says... Inver-Device... Beta version... I wonder what it's for...

Name: Karenina
Text: The thing inside looks real valuable though.

Name: Karenina
Text: There's an ID in the box... Huh? Why's it got grandpa's photo on it?

Name: Karenina
Text: Huh? Where's all that stuff I just found?

Name: Karenina
Text: Eek... It's getting late. I should head back...

Name: Karenina
Text: What's this? It looks like a remote control, for... this Robo Bug.

Name: Karenina
Text: It looks unstable, like it'd explode any minute... Let me try...

Name: Karenina
Text: Wow! It actually moved!

Name: Karenina
Text: That was a big explosion!

Name: Karenina
Text: I think it broke something... Hope no one was hurt...

Name: Watanabe
Text: The only person who can save you... is yourself. Got it.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Where you see scrap metal, I see trophies!

Name: Abnormal Corrupted
Text: ...than... my... son...

Name: Girl
Text: ...Father...?

Name: Bianca
Text: I will not allow anyone to get hurt!

Name: Bianca
Text: I will protect you all, until the end!

Name: Soldier
Text: Where'd they all go...?

Name: Watanabe
Text: The snow looks strange.

Name: Bianca
Text: This is something a priest would wear...

Name: Bianca
Text: ...Father Snow?

Name: Bianca
Text: No! The children!

Name: Kamui
Text: ...Who ARE you?
I'm the one who is going to save you.

Name: Kamui
Text: I... don't need saving.
That is not for you to decide.

Name: Nanami
Text: That's not surprising!

Name: Nanami
Text: Anyway, let's take a closer look...

Name: Nanami
Text: Hello! Can you hear me?

Name: Injured Construct
Text: Constructs from... Babylonia? They fooled you too, huh...? Watch out, behind you!

Name: Nanami
Text: Hold on while Nanami takes care of these guys. Be right back!

Name: Injured Construct
Text: Scavengers made this place... using the Corrupted. It's a Construct hunting ground...

Name: Injured Construct
Text: A girl hid me here and gave me this energy cell to keep me going...

Name: Nanami
Text: I knew it... Don't worry. I'll take it from here!

Name: Nanami
Text: So high Punishing levels! Did you come chasing after the traces of Construct remains, all the way from the surface?

Name: Nanami
Text: Hey! You there! It's not okay to destroy Nanami's favorite ruins and hurt Nanami's friends!

Name: Investigator Ryan
Text: Good timing. The energy cell will power me up for a while. I can help you!

Name: Investigator Ryan
Text: The hunting ground and the Scavengers... There's more to this than what meets the eye.

Name: Investigator Ryan
Text: It was human Scavengers that attacked me... but the girl who saved me was a human Scavenger too...

Name: Investigator Ryan
Text: Thanks to you guys I'll be able to make my report in person.

Name: Investigator Ryan
Text: I'll tell them everything, about the assault on the Fortress... You were amazing by the way!

Name: Nanami
Text: Ohoho! Of course, Nanami IS amazing! Oh... Amy, are you okay?

Name: Investigator Ryan
Text: The girl who saved me... Has she... passed out?

Name: Corrupted
Text: Power, POWER!!!

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: Is that... a Construct? Thank goodness!

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: After we were shot down, the Corrupted rushed us. We can't hold out much longer!

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: You're here to help us, right?

Name: Corrupted
Text: Devour... Target Construct...

Name: Roland
Text: After these scum found Lucia... they were like hounds on a blood trail... And now they're even in my way...

Name: Roland
Text: Do you not know that this belongs to Miss Luna?

Name: Roland
Text: Stand back.

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: Sorry, we're on a top-priority escort mission. Only team members can approach the client.

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: Duty calls, friend. Move aside. We don't want any trouble.

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: What are you doing? Aren't you here to help us?

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: Wait... This one's full of Punishing Virus! We've got contact!!!

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: Thanks for the rescue!

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: You're an old model, but you're pretty good. Which team are you from?

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: When this is done, I can finally go back to Babylonia, outta this hell hole.

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: I know you saved us, but please don't interfere with our mission.

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: Lucia is a hero to us. We must escort her back to Babylonia.

Name: Construct Soldier
Text: We don't know what the purpose of our mission is, but please cooperate. Don't approach Lucia.

Name: Roland
Text: I smell a rat.

Name: Roland
Text: Keep running, it'll make it more interesting, Lucia.

Name: Lucia
Text: I can't win in my current state... I've got to... get away...

Name: Lucia
Text: But... where can I go?

Name: Roland
Text: There you are.

Name: Roland
Text: I'm getting tired. Come back with me, there's a good girl. Miss Luna's waiting.

Name: Lucia
Text: Don't try to fool me!

Name: Roland
Text: Where are you going?

Name: Lucia
Text: Get away from me, you... Corrupted!

Name: Roland
Text: Hah hah... As expected of Miss Luna's...

Name: Roland
Text: So... you want to do it the hard way...

Name: Lucia
Text: Is that the sound of battle? I wonder what's going on.

Name: Lucia
Text: If I can just get through these Corrupted... I'll be able to get away...

Name: Lucia
Text: Finally... Am I free?

Name: Lucia
Text: But where should I go next...?

Name: Lucia
Text: Lu...na...
Tch, she's completely ignoring my attacks.
She seems to be drawn to Lucia, but Lucia, you...

Name: The Other Lucia
Text: I'm fine... Keep Commandant safe...

Name: Lucia
Text: Surely you feel it too... Lucia?

Name: Lucia
Text: Is that all you have, Lucia...?

Name: Lucia
Text: Enough of this nonsense!

Name: Human Soldier
Text: Wo-ah!

Name: Watanabe
Text: The Corrupted made it this far?!

Name: Watanabe
Text: We'll have to fight our way out!

Name: Cyril
Text: Pretty good, kid.

Name: Watanabe
Text: All Constructs can fight. Only some know how to fly.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Get on! Cyril, you go first!

Name: Watanabe
Text: I'll clear the runway!

Name: Watanabe
Text: Prepare for liftoff!

Name: Watanabe
Text: Cyril... It's not that I don't trust you...

Name: Watanabe
Text: But let's turn on the force field, just in case.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Let's see... should be the start button first...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Re-enter command, command code:\nContra\nConfirm again after entering the code.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Enemy in range. Enter combat mode!

Name: Watanabe
Text: Tsk! No time to get the force field up!

Name: Fighter Craft
Text: Captain! We got you!

Name: Cyril
Text: It's...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Backup!!

Name: Cyril
Text: Let's teach them some respect!

Name: Fighter Craft
Text: You'll never catch Captain Cyril!

Name: Fighter Craft
Text: Lay down suppressive fire!!!

Name: Fighter Craft
Text: We've been hit!

Name: Cyril
Text: Enough. Pull out.

Name: Fighter Craft
Text: Captain Cyril.

Name: Cyril
Text: You're no match for him.

Name: Fighter Craft
Text: Sorry, Captain...

Name: Cyril
Text: Watanabe, this is mine, as well as Bruce's fight against you!

Name: Cyril
Text: (Coughs) Guess us meat bags... can't keep up with Constructs in piloting...

Name: Cyril
Text: Too bad I already got the Stealth mode permissions for this unit!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: An island after the storm, a forlorn Prince, a song heard from afar.

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Welcome to my tale—the tale of Prince Ferdinand.

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Ah, what a desolate place this is? I, the proudest son of the King of Naples, find myself upon this foreign field!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: That damned and sudden tempest, frightening to behold, overturned a mighty galleon thirty decks in height!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Uprooting the stout mast and shredding a hundred sturdy sails,

Name: Ferdinand
Text: I don't even know if my brilliant father, the blessed King of Naples, is alive or dead!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: What sin has been committed for beloved father and son to be so cruelly torn apart?

Name: Servant
Text: Your Majesty, I am sure your father will be safe.

Name: Servant
Text: Majesty, I fear the King has been shipwrecked on another island just as we have.

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Then what are we waiting for? Naples cannot last one day without its King, nor can I last one day without my beloved father!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Pass me my sword! No treacherous wood nor wild beast can stand in my way!

Name: Servant & Servant
Text: Yes, Your Majesty. We will lay down our lives for you!

Name: Caliban
Text: Swine! This is a province of gods and fairies, not a place for worthless bags of skin like you!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: ...Am I imagining things? Don't tell me, my ears were drowned by the sea?

Name: Servant
Text: Majesty! This creature called you a swine!

Name: Servant
Text: Majesty! This creature called you a worthless bag of skin!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Ingrates! Do I not treat you with kindness every day? How dare you insult me and blame it on someone else!

Name: Servant & Servant
Text: Mercy, Majesty!

Name: Caliban
Text: Look at these ugly mortals, covered in fair skin, but filled with dirty secrets!

Name: Caliban
Text: Alas... Only the magician's daughter can be said to be truly beautiful!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Shallow monster! Not even fair maids are safe from your predation!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Hahahaha, the battle has only served to stir my blood! Now to rid the world of another evil!

Name: Caliban
Text: ROOARR—!!! I shall smash you into pulp, pipsqueak!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Ha, ha... Not bad for a weak monster.

Name: Caliban
Text: Look at the pipsqueak, waving his toothpick around like he's a real Knight.

Name: Servant & Servant
Text: Yes, Your Majesty! You can do it!
Stop!

Name: Caliban
Text: Hark, that voice, sweet as the blood of my quarry. A beautiful angel approaches!

Name: Miranda
Text: A fragrant island, a beautiful princess, guest of the storm.

Name: Miranda
Text: Welcome to my tale—the tale of Princess Miranda.

Name: Miranda
Text: The tempest has pass'd, the storm clouds have parted, sunshine spills upon the golden earth.

Name: Miranda
Text: Blessed Goddess! Your faithful servants sing your praises!

Name: Miranda
Text: Wait! Is that sound of fairies conversing upon the wind?

Name: Miranda
Text: Listen. The sounds of battle over yonder.

Name: Miranda
Text: Is that the voice Caliban I can hear! Oh no! I must go and see!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Ha, ha... Not bad for a weak monster.

Name: Caliban
Text: Look at the pipsqueak, waving his toothpick around like he's a real Knight.

Name: Servant & Servant
Text: Yes, Your Majesty! You can do it!

Name: Miranda
Text: Stop!

Name: Miranda
Text: I called out without thinking... what shall I say next?

Name: Miranda
Text: Caliban is a powerful warrior! I never thought a mortal man would rival him!

Name: Miranda
Text: Oh! His countenance is so determined; his eyes are so deep!

Name: Miranda
Text: He is looking right at me! Be still my beating heart!

Name: Miranda
Text: It can't go on! Miranda, breathe deep! And speak in a steady voice—

Name: Miranda
Text: Stop this pointless fighting!

Name: King Alonso
Text: Prospero? What's going on?

Name: Prospero
Text: You traitor! Show yourself before your honorable king.

Name: Antonio
Text: Such filthy rumor. Does it come out of a demon's mouth?

Name: Prospero
Text: You are guilty of defying your king. It has been evidenced and no one could screen you anymore.

Name: Antonio
Text: Since you already found it out, only death upon you can spare my punishment!

Name: Abastian
Text: Let's not waste our time on this ignorant fool.

Name: Trinculo
Text: We'll just have to make them unable to talk.

Name: Antonio
Text: Ah! Don't touch me. I'm just a piece of rotten flesh!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: I'm here to declare, in the name of the god's divinity and justice, that the rebel has been defeated!

Name: Miranda
Text: Ferdinand! I know you are the one who has filled the space in my heart!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Oh, Miranda, stay calm. We still have a long time for this.

Name: Caliban
Text: No! I... won't allow it! Miranda's heart belongs to me!

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Pathetic monster, your wish is meaningless.

Name: Ferdinand
Text: Miranda's heart already belongs to me. It is an unshakable truth.

Name: Miranda
Text: I can't hold myself together anymore...

Name: Miranda
Text: Caliban, I'm telling you I won't spend my life with you.

Name: Caliban
Text: Miranda... What a pitiful woman!

Name: Bianca
Text: Toby, what's wrong?

Name: Toby
Text: I don't have much time left... Can you do me a favor?

Name: Toby
Text: I heard the rumors, but I believe Bianca isn't that kind of person.

Name: Toby
Text: Please pick up that bow...

Name: Bianca
Text: Toby...

Name: Toby
Text: I can't remember what has happed. When I woke up, I've already found myself in this church.

Name: Toby
Text: It must've been God's will. At the last moment of my life... meet... ugh...

Name: Toby
Text: Meet... Ugh... Agh...

Name: Bianca
Text: Toby—Toby!

Name: Toby
Text: It's... too late... ARRRGGH!

Name: Bianca
Text: No...

Name: Bianca
Text: Sorry...

Name: Bianca
Text: Wh—What are you talking about?

Name: Toby
Text: Please... accept my bold request...

Name: Toby
Text: Kill me...

Name: Toby
Text: Thank... you... Bianca...

Name: Bianca
Text: Will this relieve Toby's pain...

Name: Bianca
Text: Sorry... for inflicting that kind of pain on you.

Name: Bianca
Text: I'll come with you soon, as a human, not someone else's weapon.

Name: Wen
Text: How disappointing.

Name: Wen
Text: Farewell.

Name: Sophia
Text: This time, I'll protect everyone!

Name: Sophia
Text: Last one. We're safe now.

Name: Sophia
Text: Why did I hear the boss tell me to run off?

Name: Sophia
Text: ...Now's not the time to think about this.

Name: Sophia
Text: Run... Where's everyone?

Name: Sophia
Text: A luxurious carriage...

Name: Sophia
Text: Jamilah doesn't deserve this.

Name: Sophia
Text: Jamilah, I found it.

Name: Sophia
Text: But those guards... We can't just leave them here.

Name: Guard
Text: You...

Name: Guard
Text: Just like the leader said...

Name: Chrome
Text: I should be able to hack into that device next to the gate and activate it...

Name: Chrome
Text: If only I can have more time...

Name: All
Text: Leader, the Corrupted are coming!

Name: Chrome
Text: I knew they would notice us...

Name: Chrome
Text: Everyone, deploy your weapons! Formation B5!

Name: Chrome
Text: But we'll only end up being surrounded if we defend here.

Name: Chrome
Text: (There's only one way to survive and become Smith.)

Name: Chrome
Text: I'm going to hack into the gate's control system. Enemies will come out from inside, and I'm counting on you to take care of them!

Name: All
Text: Roger!

Name: Skip the animation?
Text: <color=#ff6633>Move joystick up or down to</color> select, then tap the <color=#ff6633>Interact button</color> to confirm.\n<color=#ff6633>Skipping selection doesn't affect special events.</color>

Name: Chrome
Text: I can only let one of them defend one way. How should I assign them...

Name: Chrome
Text: First of all, let me examine their strengths again.

Name: Chrome
Text: This is Ace (Rank C), <color=#ff6633>the best</color> of the three. He has never let me down.

Name: Chrome
Text: This is Taro (Rank D). He's <color=#ff6633>quite good</color> and has completed many missions.

Name: Chrome
Text: And here's Dika (Rank E), a <color=#ff6633>rookie</color> on his very first mission. He's still got a lot more to learn.

Name: Chrome
Text: What about the enemies...

Name: Chrome
Text: There's no doubt that the enemies are <color=#ff6633>elites</color> and <color=#ff6633>stronger than us</color>.

Name: Chrome
Text: This one with a lance is <color=#ff6633>extremely dangerous</color>. He's a lot stronger than Ace (Rank C), even I can't guarantee that I will win.

Name: Chrome
Text: This one using arrows is <color=#ff6633>quite dangerous</color>. Taro (Rank D) is probably no match for him, but Ace (Rank C) should be able to stop him.

Name: Chrome
Text: This one with twin blades is <color=#ff6633>very mediocre</color>. He's better than Dika (Rank E), but weaker than Taro (Rank D).

Name: Chrome
Text: Based on the available information, my answer is...

Name: Chrome
Text: Must I sacrifice one of them?

Name: Chrome
Text: Time's running out. I must make a decision...

Name: Chrome
Text: Send Ace (Rank C) to...\n(<color=#ff6633>Move Joystick up or down</color> to select, then tap the <color=#ff6633>Interact button</color> to confirm selection).

Name: Chrome
Text: Send Taro (Rank D) to...\n(<color=#ff6633>Move Joystick up or down</color> to select, then tap the <color=#ff6633>Interact button</color> to confirm selection).

Name: Chrome
Text: Send Dika (Rank E) to...\n(<color=#ff6633>Move Joystick up or down</color> to select, then tap the <color=#ff6633>Interact button</color> to confirm selection).

Name: Chrome
Text: The decision is made. I need to do my part now.

Name: Chrome
Text: (Smith must pick up every useful piece to become the perfect monster.)

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: I am back!

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: Sorry... Leader...

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: No! I can't fall yet!

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: It's too powerful! There's no way I can win... But I'll never let you get close to Leader!

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: Die...with me!

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: Finally... I win...

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: Gargh! Why can't I win?

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: No! I can't fall yet!

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: It's too powerful! There's no way I can win... But I'll never let you get close to Leader!

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: Die...with me!

Name: Dika (Rank E)
Text: I must...go back to Leader!

Name: Dika (Rank E)
Text: I...couldn't do anything...

Name: Dika (Rank E)
Text: No! I can't fall yet!

Name: Dika (Rank E)
Text: It's too powerful! There's no way I can win... But I'll never let you get close to Leader!

Name: Dika (Rank E)
Text: Die...with me!

Name: Chrome
Text: I will not let my members die in vain...

Name: Chrome
Text: Ace (Rank C), Taro (Rank D), and Dika (Rank E). I will never forget you.

Name: Chrome
Text: Dika (Rank E). We will avenge you!

Name: Chrome
Text: Ace (Rank C), let's avenge Taro (Rank D) and Dika (Rank E)!

Name: Chrome
Text: Taro (Rank D), let's avenge Ace (Rank C) and Dika (Rank E)!

Name: Chrome
Text: Am I the only one left...

Name: Chrome
Text: All gathered up. This is the last fight!

Name: Chrome
Text: (Cough...)

Name: Ace (Rank C) & Taro (Rank D)
Text: Roger!

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: Roger!

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: Roger!

Name: Chrome
Text: This is what I really want... I want to be Chrome of Strike Hawk, not Smith!

Name: Chrome
Text: Kamui, I'm joining the battle. Wait for my order!

Name: Ace (Rank C) & Taro (Rank D)
Text: Great! It's Strike Hawk!

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: Thanks... I never thought I could meet Strike Hawk.

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: Strike Hawk... Let's fight together!

Name: Kamui
Text: Been waiting for you, Leader!

Name: Chrome
Text: Follow me!

Name: Ace (Rank C)
Text: I must not fall. I can't let Dika (Rank E) down...!

Name: Taro (Rank D)
Text: I will survive this. I must!

Name: Hiro
Text: Lucia, can you hear me?

Name: Lucia
Text: Copy. What's the situation over there?

Name: Hiro
Text: Don't worry about me. I noticed that you were trying to take Riot one-on-one. Just remember to watch out for his laser.

Name: Lucia
Text: Laser?

Name: Hiro
Text: You'll know when you see it. Anyway, take care, I'm gonna keep running.

Name: Lucia
Text: Okay.

Name: Lucia
Text: *Gasp*... Never thought this could be the laser he mentioned.

Name: Murol
Text: Nonetheless, the victory is ours. Commandant, we should ask Hiro to bring back the Corrupted.

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant?

Name: Lucia
Text: It's not over yet!

Name: Lucia
Text: Something just ran past...

Name: Lucia
Text: Is this inevitable?

Name: Lucia
Text: I knew I had to face you all to complete the synchronization of my M.I.N.D...

Name: Lucia
Text: Kamui, Chrome, Watanabe...

Name: Lucia
Text: Sorry, but I have to pass!

Name: Lucia
Text: The Purifying Force. Bianca, Karenina, and a few others in my memory.

Name: Lucia
Text: Whether we used to be enemies doesn't matter.

Name: Lucia
Text: Right now, you are my comrades.

Name: Lucia
Text: By the way, there's something I wanted to tell you long ago.

Name: Lucia
Text: Karenina, you're a lot better than me.

Name: Lucia
Text: Ayla, Sophia, Nanami. You are very interesting...

Name: Lucia
Text: I saw a lot in you, and learned a lot too.

Name: Lucia
Text: Now is the time to turn what I learned into my strength!

Name: Lucia
Text: Lee, you're always thinking, sometimes you think too much and miss the chance. Liv, you worry a lot and make yourself very tired.

Name: Lucia
Text: Two of you are just like me. We don't know how to express ourselves.

Name: Lucia
Text: What we had in common brought us together. That's why we are Gray Raven.

Name: Lucia
Text: Too bad I have to defeat you. I need to fly higher now!

Name: Lucia
Text: Right. These are your memories too. And that's exactly why—

Name: Lucia
Text: I want you to disappear from my M.I.N.D.!

Name: Lucia
Text: Right, Plume... You are the last obstacle.

Name: Lucia
Text: You are everything that I have ever accumulated. The things that I cherish the most...

Name: Lucia
Text: I really want to keep this memory if possible. I want it to always be mine.

Name: Lucia
Text: But I must give all I have for this battle.

Name: Lucia
Text: That's why... Lucia, you must disappear from this world, for the sake of Commandant!

Name: Vera
Text: Captain, pull back now!

Name: Squadron Leader
Text: Vera, I told you to stay at the rear. What are you doing here?

Name: Vera
Text: Not now! Get in the combat zone, quick!

Name: Squadron Leader
Text: Don't be silly. There's nothing for us there, nothing but danger!

Name: Vera
Text: That's not what I'm talking about... Damn it, am I disconnected?!

Name: Squadron Leader
Text: Wow, you just had to come, didn't you? Even after I specifically told you not to...

Name: Construct Member
Text: Boss, we've got company.

Name: Squadron Leader
Text: What?!

Name: Squadron Leader
Text: What's this?

Name: Vera
Text: The Corrupted are gathering up faster than I imagined... Dammit!

Name: Vera
Text: I can't handle this...

Name: Vera
Text: We can't stay here. More are coming.

Name: Vera
Text: Gotta get into the virus zone!

Name: Familiar Construct
Text: We bought enough time. Go, Vera, retreat with the citizens.

Name: Vera
Text: You're the ones who should retreat, not me... I've shed enough tears for you!

Name: Familiar Construct
Text: We lost. Give up, Vera.

Name: Vera
Text: How... How did it come to this?!

Name: Vera
Text: Huff... Huff...

Name: Familiar Construct
Text: Save your strength, Vera. More are on their way. We're goners now.

Name: Vera
Text: Shut up!

Name: Familiar Construct
Text: Vera... Thank you.

Name: Construct Soldier A
Text: Go help the others... I'm fine.

Name: Construct Soldier B
Text: This should buy us some time...

Name: Familiar Construct
Text: This... This is hopeless...

Name: Construct Soldier A
Text: I can't do this... anymore...

Name: Construct Soldier B
Text: Huff... Huff... I can't... breathe!

Name: Soldier
Text: Hey, Camu, where are you going?!

Name: Camu
Text: I'd rather work alone. You guys keep sticking together!

Name: Soldier
Text: Wait!

Name: Camu
Text: Master said I could become an advanced combatant, but I'm not sure about it.

Name: Camu
Text: And those aircraft are like surveillance cameras.

Name: Corrupted
Text: Urgh!!!

Name: Camu
Text: Right on time!

Name: Camu
Text: The Corrupted in the city have been surrounded as planned, right?

Name: Pilot
Text: Blow them up!

Name: Camu
Text: What?!

Name: Camu
Text: What's going on here?

Name: Soldier
Text: Cough...

Name: Camu
Text: Hey, where are you guys?!

Name: Soldier
Text: Run, Camu!

Name: Camu
Text: Shit! Shrapnel did a number on me. Gonna be a while before I recover from this!

Name: Camu
Text: I will not die here!

Name: Camu
Text: Let's divide and conquer! I'll take the lead!

Name: Soldier
Text: Understood!

Name: Mao Zhen
Text: Go to hell, you rotten pieces of Corrupted!

Name: Camu
Text: Master... no, uh, Mao Zhen!

Name: Camu
Text: Mao Zhen, I knew it was you!!!

Name: Mao Zhen
Text: Don't take it personally, Camu. I'm just carrying out orders.

Name: Mao Zhen
Text: (Camu... Do I still have a chance?)

Name: Camu
Text: Mao Zhen! Mao Zhen!!!

Name: Mao Zhen
Text: I told you to stay focused in battle.

Name: Camu
Text: Arghhh!!!

Name: Rosetta
Text: The bionics could be hiding in unexpected places.

Name: Rosetta
Text: I'll have to find and defeat them all.

Name: Rosetta
Text: So they can't hurt people who accidentally enter the forest.

Name: Rosetta
Text: Finally, all the lurking bionics have been defeated.

Name: Rosetta
Text: This area should be clear. Time to follow the footprints and keep moving.

Name: Rosetta
Text: I won't let you die, Grandpa. We will go home together!

Name: Rosetta
Text: I can barely move... But I can't stop here!

Name: Rosetta
Text: I know these bionics...

Name: Rosetta
Text: They must have been hiding here ever since I first met Lisa!

Name: Rosetta
Text: (If only I'd destroyed them all back then...)

Name: Pfaff
Text: Rosetta... Are you around...?

Name: Rosetta
Text: Grandpa! I'm here!

Name: Pfaff
Text: Do you know...? You were born with a blessing.

Name: Pfaff
Text: Coming to the world, you had already saved me, as well as your parents.

Name: Rosetta
Text: My... parents? You never told me...

Name: Pfaff
Text: They brought you to me out of a nightmare.

Name: Pfaff
Text: No matter what they did, you can take pride in them.

Name: Pfaff
Text: So never blame them or yourself. Do you understand? Cough...

Name: Rosetta
Text: I got it! Stop exerting yourself, Grandpa!

Name: Musashi VI
Text: {0110<color=#FF0000>0</color>011<color=#FF0000>0</color>111<color=#FF0000>00</color>1<color=#FF0000>0</color>011<color=#0000FF>000</color>01<color=#0000FF>0</color>11<color=#0000FF>00</color>10<color=#FFFF00>00</color>11<color=#FFFF00>0</color>11<color=#FFFF00>000</color>11<color=#FFFF00>0</color>0101} Activating command—enemies sighted. Eliminate them.

Name: Villier
Text: Take it easy. Just hit it a few times to paralyze it, so I can check who did this.

Name: Qu
Text: I'll try.

Name: Villier
Text: Good. Now it can't move.

Name: Villier
Text: Cra... Hmm...

Name: Yin
Text: Are you alone?

Name: Qu
Text: Yes.

Name: Yin
Text: I see. What a pity. You should have run away like that brat.

Name: Qu
Text: A ruler would never do that.

Name: Yin
Text: Haha, right, ruler. This country doesn't need two rulers.

Name: Yin
Text: Farewell, freak.

Name: Yin
Text: Useless idiots. I shall end it all.

Name: Changyu
Text: There seems to be more guards around... The auction must be starting soon.

Name: Changyu
Text: I must find Huainan before it starts.

Name: Uncle Fu
Text: Hey you, stop! Take your junks away!

Name: Changyu
Text: Um... Okay.

Name: Changyu
Text: Can this ID card open the doors in the cabin?

Name: Changyu
Text: Maybe I can use it later...

Name: Evil Merchant
Text: I... I remember you! You conned me last time, stupid brat!

Name: Evil Merchant
Text: Who was that... Huh? Where's my ID card?

Name: Evil Merchant
Text: W-with this one... Hehe... I can take all the confiscated goods that Kowloong Crew left in the warehouse... *Burp*

Name: Evil Merchant
Text: Whatcha looking at? Get lost! I'm enjoying me d-drinks!

Name: Huainan
Text: You shouldn't have come, Changyu.

Name: Changyu
Text: Say that to yourself!

Name: Huainan
Text: ...I have never doubted you.

Name: Huainan
Text: Take care of yourself.

Name: System Voice
Text: ...Record HNTI022858-1006

Name: System Voice
Text: ...Calling. Count 1006.
There's a night market on the deck. I can only sneak into this place while most guards are relocated.
I saw a woman on the way here. She was selling her organs just to not be thrown off the ship.
Her child was lying on the deck, dying. But she didn't even look at him.
All she did was to kneel and beg the merchant, asking for a tiny chance to extend her pathetic life.
Everyone on this ship has gone crazy. If anyone ever gets this message, please, send me a reply. I'm begging you.

Name: System Voice
Text: ...Record HNTI195607-1015
I found "him." Both the age and details match well.

Name: System Voice
Text: ...Record HNTI210843-1017
It's been a month since I last sent a message seeking help.
I was almost deceived by the illusion he brought. Pathetic. Miserable. I hate every single thing about this place.
Nobody can save anybody here.
Nobody can save me. No one. Only myself can.

Name: System Voice
Text: ...Record HNTI222208-1297
Am I getting crazy? Why? Why? Whywhywhywhywyywy

Name: System Voice
Text: Record HNTI032500-1298
This is my last message.
I won't change my mind again.

Name: Huainan
Text: Once you have suspicion, it will grow inside you.

Name: Huainan
Text: ...One day, you will understand that feeling.

Name: Huainan
Text: Changyu... Do not lose yourself anymore.

Name: Huainan
Text: Still... I cannot do it...

Name: Sister
Text: Luna... Kill them all for your sister!

Name: Luna
Text: For you...

Name: Luna
Text: Sis... Are you okay...? Sis...

Name: Sister
Text: Why is everything attacking me?!

Name: Sister
Text: Don't come to me... Go away!

Name: Sister
Text: What are you doing?! I'm hurt!

Name: Luna
Text: Sorry! Sis, are you okay?

Name: Sister
Text: How useless...

Name: Sister
Text: Whoa! Stop them! They're attacking me!

Name: Luna
Text: Leave Sis alone!

Name: Sister
Text: Is this... blood?! Is it my blood, or vital fluid? No...

Name: Luna
Text: Sis!

Name: Sister
Text: Help me... I don't want to die in a junkyard...

Name: Luna
Text: Ugh... Aaargh!

Name: Luna
Text: The power of the Ascension-Network is decreasing... Why?

Name: Luna
Text: She looks a bit different, but...

Name: Luna
Text: She is my sister! She's right there...

Name: Luna
Text: But who's next to her...?

Name: Luna
Text: Who are you... Why...?

Name: Channel Noise
Text: (Luna... She is too dangerous...)

Name: Luna
Text: The power of the Ascension-Network...is going haywire!

Name: Kamui
Text: This is the frontline. We have allies over there.

Name: Kamui
Text: There are just too many Corrupted here, as always.

Name: Kamui
Text: Out of my way. I don't have time to waste!

Name: Kamui
Text: Are you guys all right?

Name: Guarding Construct A
Text: Not too bad. You arrived just in time.

Name: Guarding Construct B
Text: Thanks.

Name: Kamui
Text: No problem. Let's finish them off together.

Name: Thompson
Text: Don't push yourself too far. Hide behind us Support Constructs whenever you spot danger.

Name: Wanshi
Text: Yeah...

Name: Guarding Construct A
Text: Sorry... I didn't expect there would be enemies with enhanced camouflage. They crossed our frontline defense.

Name: Thompson
Text: No worries. Thank you for holding the position.

Name: Thompson
Text: Wanshi, he needs some emergency maintenance. I'll cover you.

Name: Wanshi
Text: Understood.

Name: Guarding Construct A
Text: Thanks.

Name: Guarding Construct B
Text: Technician, Thompson. I'm counting on you two.

Name: Wanshi
Text: (Panting)

Name: Thompson
Text: Leave it to me, Wanshi. You take a break.

Name: Wanshi
Text: ...Yeah.

Name: Guarding Construct A
Text: Gargh, even these Corrupted have enhanced camouflage...

Name: Guarding Construct B
Text: Are our allies back from the frontline yet? We can't hold too long...

Name: Thompson
Text: Wanshi... Run in the opposite direction.

Name: Thompson
Text: Go to the frontline... Our main force is there...

Name: Wanshi
Text: Thompson! Guys!

Name: Construct A
Text: It's coming!

Name: Construct A
Text: Fall back...

Name: Construct B
Text: It's too dangerous here... You must go...

Name: Construct C
Text: Leave, now...

Name: Construct D
Text: I cannot fall... yet...

Name: Construct E
Text: This shard... is mankind's hope... I'm counting on... you...

Name: Selena
Text: I need to leave this place as soon as possible.

Name: Selena
Text: Must not let Korolev find me...

Name: Selena
Text: I must bring the shard back to Babylonia. Just a little longer...

Name: Selena
Text: I must stay strong, until the last moment.

Name: Selena
Text: Is this a terminal... to control the electronic lock?

Name: Selena
Text: (Operating)

Name: Selena
Text: Great, my computing power can open it.

Name: Selena
Text: (Operating)

Name: Selena
Text: The door is closed...

Name: Selena
Text: Safe at last...

Name: Korolev
Text: Korolev would like to issue a gentle reminder to children visiting the space station. Please follow the rules and regulations and listen to your guide.

Name: Korolev
Text: Children who fail to follow the instructions will be threated as invading germs.

Name: Korolev
Text: Next, I shall demonstrate...

Name: Korolev
Text: How an immune cell captures and destroys the invading germs!

Name: Selena
Text: I can't waste my time on these things.
Immune cell has found a germ.

Name: Chrome
Text: Squad Two is too depleted and needs to be able to withdraw quietly without too much engagement.

Name: Chrome
Text: The remaining Corrupted must be destroyed here before the reinforcements come.

Name: Chrome
Text: The threat in this area has been eliminated. Squad Two, report your evacuation status and location!

Name: Construct A
Text: ...Our... evac... task... disrupt...

Name: Construct A
Text: ...Implement...

Name: System Voice
Text: The communication signal is lost.

Name: Chrome
Text: Simulate their route based on terrain and the Corrupted distribution... Narrow down their coordinates.

Name: Chrome
Text: That way?!

Name: Chrome
Text: Only by moving to D7 can the King escape the dilemma of Fork by the White Queen.

Name: Chrome
Text: Even though this may put A8's Rook in danger.

Name: Chrome
Text: The Queen now at C4 has eliminated the possibility of Kingside Castling.

Name: Chrome
Text: He will definitely move a Pawn to F3 in response.

Name: Chrome
Text: Which is exactly what I need.

Name: Chrome
Text: The Knight at D4 will always be the threat of Checkmate Queen-side.

Name: Chrome
Text: Even if the white pieces hold the advantage, the black is not at a disadvantage.

Name: Chrome
Text: Look to the future while watching the present.

Name: Chrome
Text: We focus on different things, and on the chessboard, there is always one side who will see farther.

Name: Chrome
Text: They white really chose to move to D3, cutting the Checkmate.

Name: Chrome
Text: But now, the black Bishop has moved to E7, and the Rook at H8 is threating the Queen at A8.

Name: Chrome
Text: I couldn't beat my father at first because I was so determined to "become" Smith.

Name: Chrome
Text: But only by "outplaying" Smith could I really see the possibility of winning this game.

Name: Chrome
Text: Creating a new path by being "Chrome".

Name: Chrome
Text: Father... This is my choice.

Name: System
Text: Construct field test—Countdown—Begin.

Name: Corrupted
Text: Rargh—!

Name: Kurono Leader
Text: Don't blink... and watch your masterpiece work, Yarha.

Name: Kurono Leader
Text: Wonderful, wonderful... System, launch Musashi IX!

Name: Yarha
Text: What...?! No! That's a level-seven prototype! It's not calibrated—oh my god, you've launched it!

Name: Yarha
Text: I've got the test result—No. 21 has passed the highest level of the field test. We can stop the program now!

Name: Yarha
Text: No. 21! Stop attacking—Oh, no, she's out of control!

Name: Kurono Leader
Text: Dammit! Stop attacking now! Stay where you are! The security is coming!

Name: Kurono Leader
Text: NO! My Musashi! Activate the emergency protection system! Somebody grab the damn kid!

Name: Vera
Text: Damn it... I can't get through to headquarters either!

Name: Vera
Text: Enough is enough... Kurono...

Name: Vera
Text: Backup is on its way. No. 21, you retreat first!

Name: No. 21
Text: What will you do?

Name: Vera
Text: Daedalus uses the same defense system as Kurono. If we don't directly destroy those defenses, neither of us will get out.

Name: Vera
Text: So leave that to me... I'm a lot more experienced in dealing with Kurono than you.

Name: Vera
Text: All right, get out of my way!

Name: No. 21
Text: ...Understood.

Name: No. 21
Text: Comms channel... works now.

Name: Comms
Text: Bzzzz—

Name: No. 21
Text: This is No. 21, requesting backup. There are many enemies underground.

Name: Comms
Text: Bzzzz—Copy. We can't send reinforcements. Evacuate as soon as possible.

Name: No. 21
Text: You can't? Why...

Name: Comms
Text: Repeat…Bzzzz…Evacuate ASAP

Name: No. 21
Text: But, we're trapped!

Name: Comms
Text: Beep—

Name: No. 21
Text: ...You are still fighting.

Name: No. 21
Text: I can't leave you alone.

Name: Vera
Text: No. 21, didn't you hear me? Get out of here! That's an order!

Name: No. 21
Text: Roger...

Name: Vera
Text: No. 21, didn't you hear me? Get out of here! That's an order!

Name: No. 21
Text: An order? What does that mean?

Name: Vera
Text: Hmph... Playing dumb, right?

Name: Vera
Text: Don't you know my nick name? They call me "Death". Any Construct I team up with dies in the end. You want a challenge too?!

Name: No. 21
Text: Challenge? I'm good at challenge.

Name: Vera
Text: You are right... Your reputation is no better than mine.

Name: Vera
Text: You want to see who's crazier? I'm not going to lose.

Name: No. 21
Text: I'm ready!

Name: Vera
Text: Don't dilly-dally! Do you want you and me to die here?!

Name: Vera
Text: Are you deaf? I say, Get out!

Name: Vera
Text: There's something underneath...

Name: Vera
Text: This is the last area where soldiers haven't retreated yet.

Name: Vera
Text: Hey! Is there anyone here?!
Go... The Corrupted...

Name: Vera
Text: Grab your weapons. I do not permit you to give up yet!

Name: Soldier Tom
Text: I'm still alive...? What about the others? Captain... Carter... Eder...

Name: Captain Hiro
Text: I remember this spear... But why...

Name: Soldier Carter
Text: Is everyone... alright? Where's Eder...

Name: Captain Hiro
Text: Thank you... red-haired Construct... If it weren't for you...

Name: Vera
Text: Just cut the crap and retreat if you don't want to die.

Name: Soldier Tom
Text: But Captain, Eder...

Name: Soldier Carter
Text: Don't worry about him... He probably already recalled. Let's go.

Name: Soldier Eder
Text: I'm sorry... I wasn't brave enough to recall in the end...

Name: Vera
Text: Well, that timidness sometimes saves lives on the battlefield.

Name: Vera
Text: Now get and follow my banner's lead! We're breaking through!

Name: Sister
Text: You want a warm hug? Here, fall asleep in my arms...

Name: Sister
Text: God's love offers salvation.

Name: Sister
Text: Seeker of Light.

Name: Sister
Text: Tests of faith are often full of thorns.

Name: Sister
Text: Keep on going.

Name: Sister
Text: God loves all beings, saves all beings, abandons all beings...

Name: Sister
Text: Lord, have you abandoned me?

Name: Sister
Text: I give to you everything. My heart. My soul. My life.

Name: Sister
Text: What is love?

Name: Sister
Text: We are on Blessed Ground.

Name: Sister
Text: God bless.

Name: Sister
Text: Is this what God wants from me?

Name: Lucia
Text: Is that a Musashi IX in the middle?

Name: Camu
Text: You may hurt me. But my people will avenge me!

Name: Camu
Text: STAY BACK!!! AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH—

Name: Camu
Text: Let's fight!!!

Name: Camu
Text: Fourth line

Name: Lucia
Text: Press left to start, press right to view.

Name: Lucia
Text: Press the button to start a 10-second blitz. For 10 seconds, any damage taken will send you to the last save point.

Name: Lucia
Text: Press the button to view Trap frequency.

Name: Lucia
Text: Press the button to stop viewing.

Name: Celica
Text: Attention Commandants, this mission is a Stronghold assault.

Name: Celica
Text: The enemy has already deployed defenses along the route, but we only have partial enemy intel.

Name: Celica
Text: Therefore, choose your line-up carefully.

Name: Celica
Text: We have arrived at the enemy stronghold. Powerful enemies await.

Name: Celica
Text: Contact! Enemies appeared!

Name: Celica
Text: Today we're clearing this crowded Corrupted zone.

Name: Celica
Text: There are all kinds of Corrupted here and they come in huge numbers too. It's gonna be rough.

Name: Celica
Text: They're about to attack!

Name: Celica
Text: Clear Requirement: Kill a total of 100 enemies.

Name: Celica
Text: 10 enemies killed, 90 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 20 enemies killed, 80 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 30 enemies killed, 70 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 40 enemies killed, 60 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 50 enemies killed, 50 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 60 enemies killed, 40 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 70 enemies killed, 30 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 80 enemies killed, 20 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: 90 enemies killed, 10 more to go.

Name: Celica
Text: All enemies have been killed. You did well today.

Name: Celica
Text: Training Mission: <color=#ff5656>Destroy all targets within the designated time</color>.

Name: Celica
Text: Training Mission: <color=#ff5656>Destroy all targets. Give priority to marked Corrupted</color>.

Name: Celica
Text: Training Mission: <color=#ff5656>Destroy all targets within the designated time</color>.

Name: Celica
Text: <color=#ff5656>You have left the designated combat area</color>. Please return to the battlefield.

Name: Celica
Text: Hey, Commandant. There's some good news and some bad news.

Name: Celica
Text: The good news is, someone sponsored us a bunch of Cogs. We were running out.

Name: Celica
Text: The bad news is, we aren't the only ones after them.

Name: Celica
Text: We have to get our hands on these resources asap.

Name: Celica
Text: The new materials arrived today, but the transport team got sloppy and lost some along the way.

Name: Celica
Text: Could you go and salvage the missing materials for us?

Name: Celica
Text: Keep in mind, this area is not secure. Do your best to avoid all enemy contact.

Name: Celica
Text: Collect 5 crates and then extract. No need to take unnecessary risks! Good luck.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 1/7.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 2/7.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 3/7.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 4/7.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 5/7. Target achieved.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 6/7. Target exceeded.

Name: Celica
Text: Materials collected 7/7. All materials collected. Mission fully completed.

Name: Celica
Text: The enemy is systematically looting and destroying our materials!

Name: Celica
Text: 5 waves are expected. Be ready.

Name: Celica
Text: Objective: Protect materials and destroy all enemies.

Name: Celica
Text: This stage is currently being used for internal testing and is not an official stage.

Name: Kuroro
Text: A special snowball has appeared.

Name: Kuroro
Text: Someone just picked up lots of snowballs. Quick, hide!

Name: Lee
Text: Gold dust falling from the sky... I was right. Some device is sending gold dust to high altitudes.

Name: Lucia
Text: Metallic dust is sometimes used to cause electrical interference. Those mechanoids seem unaffected by it though.

Name: Lee
Text: They must be the "Mechanoid Guards" Browning described.

Name: Lee
Text: Avoid or attack. I'm good with either. You decide, Commandant.

Name: Lucia
Text: These guards aren't easy to deal with. I sure hope Liv is okay...

Name: Lucia
Text: I dug them up and compared their chassis numbers. They're Goldfinch units.

Name: Lucia
Text: Where I found them, there were three immobilized guards. One of them could be the "culprit".

Name: Lucia
Text: We must find the "culprit" and get to the bottom of it.

Name: Lee
Text: Maybe their remains will hold some clues.

Name: Lee
Text: Whatever made these markings... has got to be the same type of Construct...

Name: Lucia
Text: Lee, turn him over... What's that on his back?

Name: Lee
Text: ...Yep. It's a Goldfinch Inducer.

Name: Browning
Text: It's well guarded for some place that's in the middle of nowhere...

Name: Browning
Text: Frontal assault is not our thing... Give them the slip, then pick off the weak.

Name: Browning
Text: An underground facility...

Name: Goldfinch Member
Text: Browning! Multiple contacts!

Name: Browning
Text: We aren't equipped for this.

Name: Browning
Text: Pull back to the bridge!

Name: Goldfinch Member
Text: Unknown force field detected. If we continue towards the bridge, we'll get shredded...

Name: Browning
Text: Cover me while I set up a terminal to lift the field!

Name: Browning
Text: There's one more, waiting in ambush... OPEN FIRE!!!

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant, this one's different. Normally I'd suggest pulling back...

Name: Lucia
Text: But we've got to stop it emitting that distress signal.

Name: Lucia
Text: They just keep coming! There's no time! Take it down, Commandant!

Name: Lucia
Text: Lee still hasn't found Liv... Sorry. I shouldn't have been distracted...

Name: Lucia
Text: The Construct models outside are no longer used in Babylonia.

Name: Lucia
Text: I've been observing closely. There's no guards beyond the hideout. Please stay here, Commandant...

Name: Lucia
Text: I'm going to copy their combat logs. Maybe we can get some intel...

Name: Unknown Construct
Text: Gold... Gold...

Name: Unknown Construct
Text: The Queen gives us... hope.

Name: Lucia
Text: The Queen...?

Name: Lee
Text: So the Mechanoid Guards were using these secret tunnels for rapid deployment.

Name: Lee
Text: The tunnels are covered in tin, blocking electrical signals of any forces moving through them.

Name: Iron Maiden
Text: Construct... are you a royal guard, or slave?

Name: Lee
Text: You sneak along behind me and never show yourself. I almost thought you were being shy.

Name: Iron Maiden
Text: I've decided. You must be a slave.

Name: Iron Maiden
Text: The Queen... needs me...

Name: Lee
Text: She has the ability to overpower me... so why is she running?

Name: Lee
Text: Fighting on constricted terrain eliminates the enemy's numerical advantage.

Name: Lee
Text: But it doesn't leave much space for evasion.

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant, Lee and I aren't in very good shape. For this battle, you'll need to access Construct operating systems.

Name: Lucia
Text: Lower performance could cause Dodge lag and other problems. I'd feel better if you had access.

Name: Lucia
Text: If you don't mind, Commandant...

Name: Iron Maiden
Text: My dream... is over...

Name: Browning
Text: I've got to reduce Construct energy consumption... to save energy...

Name: Liv
Text: Please stay by me when I fight.

Name: Liv
Text: Let me take care of the fighting. I'll keep you safe.

Name: Liv
Text: It's unbelievable how many guards are lurking under the sand!

Name: Liv
Text: Browning, you're in charge of the Excavator. I'll stop the guards.

Name: Liv
Text: Guards have been pushed back. Browning, is everything okay?

Name: Browning
Text: Don't come over here!

Name: Liv
Text: Huh? The combat system has security measures...?

Name: Liv
Text: Why didn't Browning mention it...?

Name: Liv
Text: Stay calm, Liv... I need to beat them to change the energy protocols.

Name: Liv
Text: ...How?!! There are no energy protocols! It's a dummy system!

Name: Watanabe
Text: So many guards... If you can't fix the defense systems, get over here! I'm in trouble!

Name: Watanabe
Text: I'll just grab one to examine.

Name: Watanabe
Text: So the siren has three alarms.

Name: Watanabe
Text: The first two alert the guards. The third one goes to a proxy terminal.

Name: Watanabe
Text: This thing is basically useless now.

Name: Bianca
Text: Why are they all kneeling here?

Name: Bianca
Text: ... Besides the battle damage, they're in pretty good shape.

Name: Bianca
Text: More guards... They just never end.

Name: Bianca
Text: Goldfinch, can your people still fight?

Name: Bianca
Text: If I win, you have to come clean with me.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Not gonna happen, because I'm not losing.

Name: Watanabe
Text: So many guards...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Let bygones be bygones. I won't follow you anymore. We should go our separate ways.

Name: Watanabe
Text: If I'm not mistaken, these engines drive those artificial sandstorms around the Golden Vortex.

Name: Watanabe
Text: But it stands to reason there must be more engines to generate so many sand storms.

Name: Watanabe
Text: My people... probably aren't trapped here.

Name: Watanabe
Text: I've been spotted! Better deal with these guys first...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Did someone rob a bank? This place is crawling with guards.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Better rush over, just in case.

Name: Bianca
Text: I'm standing right in front of them and still nothing? Maybe these Mechanoids aren't guards after all.

Name: Bianca
Text: Looks like they've got some kind of golden ring marked on them... Hard to tell what it is.

Name: Bianca
Text: What's that sound...? It's been ringing for ages...

Name: Bianca
Text: Da-da-di-da, di-di-da, di, di, da-di. What could it mean?

Name: Watanabe
Text: I'm not gonna fight you, at least not now.

Name: Watanabe
Text: This place is crawling with guards. And I only just found my people.

Name: Bianca
Text: ...Where is he?

Name: Bianca
Text: If I can flush him out, have his men draw the guards' attention, he's bound to make an appearance.

Name: Unconscious Forsaken
Text: Ah! Run! Shhh! The Warden's coming!

Name: Bianca
Text: Got to make sure those guards don't hurt him.

Name: Unconscious Forsaken
Text: Run! Run! He's coming! Run!

Name: Unconscious Forsaken
Text: I'm so scared... Leader, save me...

Name: Bianca
Text: There you are.

Name: Watanabe
Text: ...You used my people?

Name: Kamui
Text: Roland's probably cowering inside. There's no gold dust floating around in here.

Name: Kamui
Text: Fancy being brought to your knees by a spec of gold dust.

Name: Roland
Text: You're... no match for me...

Name: Kamui
Text: Whatever. I know you're gonna call in reinforcements.

Name: Kamui
Text: It doesn't matter who you send, the gold dust has turned you all into jelly!

Name: Kamui
Text: Gold dust doesn't just weaken the enemy, it interferes with their ability to tell friend from foe...

Name: Roland
Text: ...I'll just have to kill you myself!

Name: Roland
Text: ...I didn't come here to fight meaningless battles.

Name: Roland
Text: Garbage! Aim at the enemy!

Name: The Forsaken
Text: Shh... I know you... You know our leader Watanabe, right?

Name: Bianca
Text: ...You're a Forsaken?

Name: The Forsaken
Text: Quiet... Don't let the Warden hear you... He's hiding among the hostages...

Name: The Forsaken
Text: Cough... cough... Beware the Warden...

Name: Hostage
Text: ...Finally, someone has come to save us.

Name: Bianca
Text: So... you must be the "Warden". If not for the Forsaken, you might have tricked me.

Name: Hostage
Text: You dare oppose the will of the Queen!?

Name: Bianca
Text: Can you stand, human?

Name: Hostage
Text: No... I can't...

Name: Hostage
Text: Help me... Take my hand...

Name: Bianca
Text: It's okay. I'll get you out...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Everyone okay?

Name: Bianca
Text: The guards have defeated some Forsaken.

Name: Watanabe
Text: They came here to help me...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Forsaken, stand up! The battle's not over!

Name: Bianca
Text: Keep going! The battle's not over!

Name: Watanabe
Text: There's a few more left... Let me repay that volley with interest!

Name: Roland
Text: Release antibodies... and send me more guards...

Name: Roland
Text: Nithart... might be the toughest... opponent I've ever faced...

Name: Roland
Text: Still... these guards... pose no threat to an Ascendant...

Name: Nithart
Text: You put up a good fight, but you might need more antibodies.

Name: Roland
Text: Antibodies... mean nothing... to an Ascendant...

Name: Nithart
Text: You made no attempt to surrender, that's good.

Name: Nithart
Text: Show me your full strength as an Ascendant.

Name: Karenina
Text: Leave her be for a while...

Name: Karenina
Text: I can defeat the enemies safely with her barrier.

Name: Nanami
Text: Hey! How was Nanami's performance?

Name: Karenina
Text: Enough! There is still some distance away from the main building. Come with me!

Name: Nanami
Text: Alright... And you're not even praising Nanami...

Name: Nanami
Text: Ding-Ding-Dong... Ding-Ding-Dong... What are you installing, Karenina?

Name: Karenina
Text: There are so many guards. Don't tell me you're still gonna barge in by yourself.

Name: Karenina
Text: It's time for me to do some improvisation.

Name: Karenina
Text: Introducing my "automatic cannon" device. With it and my firepower, the guards pose no threat to us.

Name: Nanami
Text: So many Corrupted! So exciting! Nanami loves it!

Name: Nanami
Text: Core parts for hacking can definitely be found from these waves of Corrupted.

Name: Nanami
Text: Nanami is going to find it!

Name: Nanami
Text: Congratulations, Nanami... Core parts get!

Name: Nanami
Text: Hm...? A reinforcement request?

Name: Roland
Text: All Corrupted... Come to my coordinates... Eliminate all your obstacles...

Name: Nanami
Text: Whoa! Amazing!

Name: Nanami
Text: Your reinforcements will be right there, Roland!

Name: Karenina
Text: One transceiver terminal is not enough to avoid disruptions while rebuilding the channel.

Name: Karenina
Text: The guards are definitely gonna notice once the terminal is on... It's so damn heavy too...

Name: Karenina
Text: Where even is Nanami!

Name: Karenina
Text: Channel 1 restored in one go... Luck is on my side.

Name: Karenina
Text: Internet channel restored... for perhaps a few minutes...

Name: Karenina
Text: Whatever! I need to quickly upload the antibody's analysis report.

Name: Nanami
Text: 1, 2, 3... and the one blocked by you, there are 4 air outlets in total.

Name: Roland
Text: We can only do two of them... These guards are required for the remaining...

Name: Roland
Text: Quick! Nanami! Stuff the guards in!

Name: Roland
Text: Must have them all collapse... on the air outlets...

Name: Roland
Text: Then their mobility will be limited... after Nithart reconnects to them.

Name: Nanami
Text: Ah, Nanami has seen some of the defeated guards came alive. So they were "reconnected"!

Name: Roland
Text: That's right... Seems like only a few of them can be reconnected.

Name: Roland
Text: The influence of the antibodies weakened...

Name: Roland
Text: Nanami... Thank you! I owe you one.

Name: Nanami
Text: Naughty Roland! Hmph!

Name: Roland
Text: ...Partially utilizing the Punishing Virus is impracticable, huh. As expected.

Name: Nanami
Text: Naughty Roland, Nanami's gonna bring you home!

Name: Kamui
Text: A Construct kneeling before a guard... Is that supposed to be an insult towards us?

Name: Karenina
Text: Wait! The guard's cognition device contains the blueprint of the Golden Vortex.

Name: Karenina
Text: They were the initial builders of this spectacle in the desert.

Name: Kamui
Text: ...Can we just extract the blueprint directly? In this case, we'll know the exact route!

Name: Karenina
Text: We can't... There's an extract permission, and we only... have two chances...

Name: Karenina
Text: Also, some of the blueprints are fake...

Name: Kamui
Text: What if... we extract the fake one?

Name: Kamui
Text: Bingo! Incredible me!

Name: Karenina
Text: We were just lucky, you dimwit...

Name: Kamui
Text: That wimp has absorbed the gold dust, and that's why it became that strong...

Name: Kamui
Text: It's gonna be a tough battle...

Name: Kamui
Text: Not like it's going to stop me! Let's duke it out!

Name: Kamui
Text: If we defeat them all and collect some gold dust, we may be able to cut it down to size.

Name: Kamui
Text: Still, I need to build an equipment to spread the gold dust into the air...

Name: Kamui
Text: Man, I'm not made for this kinda work...

Name: Roland
Text: The opera of the Punishing Virus... begins...

Name: Roland
Text: All your security programs make no difference.

Name: Roland
Text: Be prepared for doom, Golden Vortex.

Name: Roland
Text: Still gonna resist...?

Name: Master-Control Program
Text: Power system crashed... Eliminating... eliminating errors...

Name: Kamui
Text: Have they noticed Nanami?

Name: Karenina
Text: Obviously! Cut the crap and come with me to protect Nanami!

Name: Karenina
Text: Hurry up! Connect the guard's system for me!

Name: Karenina
Text: Nanami is isolated and helpless, I have to get in and help her!

Name: Kamui
Text: Just put on the bio-booster arms found by Nanami! I can feel the tremendous power inside them!

Name: Kamui
Text: I should try them on the Queen's guards later!

Name: Kamui
Text: But first, I need to test the arms' strength...

Name: Karenina
Text: The only place defended by the Queen's royal guards within the whole Golden Vortex is the Queen's bedchamber.

Name: Kamui
Text: I hope their strength is worthy of their title!

Name: The Queen's Royal Guard
Text: How dare you trespass on the Queen's prohibited zone... Pay with your lives!

Name: Nanami
Text: Yeah! Nanami is going to meet Commandant real soon!

Name: Karenina
Text: But what about the front door?

Name: Kamui
Text: Don't worry. I can pry it open with one hand!

Name: Nithart
Text: Don't let go of any of them! Destroy them all!

Name: Nithart
Text: Commandant! This is your last chance!

Name: Nithart
Text: If you abandon those Constructs now, I can spare your life!

Name: Nanami
Text: There's a traitor among Nithart's guards... Nanami has met it before. It owns the door key...

Name: Lucia
Text: Traitor? Nanami, you...?

Name: Karenina
Text: Nanami has once connected to Nithart's network for a short time. If she says there's a key, there must be one.

Name: Nanami
Text: It used to be a Construct. The hole in its security system allowed it to shortly get rid of Nithart's control...

Name: Lucia
Text: Scatter! Find the Construct guard! Find the traitor!

Name: Lee
Text: I've just hacked into it, but I couldn't find any keys...

Name: Lucia
Text: Don't give up! Bianca also found a Construct guard, let's go there now!

Name: Lee
Text: Successfully hacked... but still there's no key in it...

Name: Nithart
Text: Don't ever think about hiding that from me!

Name: Nithart
Text: Guards! Quick! Obliterate the traitor with the key!

Name: Construct Guard
Text: Thank you for releasing me from Nithart's control...

Name: Karenina
Text: Too many guards here. No point wasting my energy with them...

Name: Karenina
Text: We can operate them to battle after transferring their control to my virtual control console...

Name: Karenina
Text: But I can only build one virtual control console with the materials I have...

Name: Karenina
Text: One virtual control console can only hijack one guard's control...

Name: Karenina
Text: Which one should we choose?

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant, I see Nanami on the platform far from our right side...

Name: Lee
Text: She must have dropped into the wrong tunnel and eventually fell there.

Name: Lee
Text: She's not the type to keep quiet.

Name: Lee
Text: Watch out, Nithart's guards are coming at us through the other entrance.

Name: Lucia
Text: She won't let go of us easily. So get ready to fight!

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant, Nanami is fighting alone, please closely monitor her frame's condition...

Name: Nithart
Text: Look what I've got you...

Name: Nithart
Text: Exhibit again that conceit you've shown me before, or my guards will turn you into scrap.

Name: Bianca
Text: ...Most cunning. Thankfully, I'm her opponent.

Name: Bianca
Text: I have to return to Commandant as quickly as possible.

Name: Bianca
Text: It's the last...

Name: Nithart
Text: Destroy her! This is an order from the Queen! Destroy her!

Name: Kamui
Text: The virus has damaged the security process of the energy system. Our hacking is going well so far!

Name: Kamui
Text: Implant the "anti-virus programs"...

Name: Kamui
Text: If we're able to send these anti-virus programs to the corrupted zone, the infection speed will be greatly slowed down...

Name: Kamui
Text: I've already defeated two Corrupted outside...

Name: Kamui
Text: Keep pushing! Don't lose to "yourself," Kamui!

Name: Kamui
Text: The corrupted zone is ahead...

Name: Kamui
Text: This should buy some time for the Gray Raven, right?

Name: Karenina
Text: Unable to open?! What does that mean! I managed to crack into it...

Name: Lee
Text: That's because your crack is one-way only. You can only open all security doors if you execute the crack.

Name: Lee
Text: But in that case, the guards can also get in and surround us.

Name: Lee
Text: So, apart from an "open door" function, we need a "close door" one as well. The two actions must be done at the same time.

Name: Karenina
Text: Easy-peasy! I can connect the two cracking devices to the same "repeater". Problem solved.

Name: Lee
Text: Well, repeating is the easy part. The difficult part is that the second cracking device has to connect the "closing" system.

Name: Lee
Text: As door opening and door closing are two separate systems, we can only crack it one by one.

Name: Lee
Text: Lucia and the others are defending against the guards outside. We have to crack the door closing system quickly.

Name: Lucia
Text: You need to be quick. As more and more guards are trying to break through the exterior wall, they will break through our defense soon...

Name: Karenina
Text: Right... But why did the crack fail? Definitely nothing to do with my devices.

Name: Lee
Text: Yes, Nithart crashed the system on purpose while we were cracking. That's why it failed.

Name: Lee
Text: I'll connect the door closing system to my virtual console. If she does that again, she'll be redirected to it.

Name: Karenina
Text: Operating the final crack... Security doors opened...

Name: Lucia
Text: ...Everyone, through the security door! Quick!

Name: Lucia
Text: Lee...

Name: Lee
Text: Okay. Operating the final crack... Security doors closed...

Name: Lucia
Text: Watch your front and back, the guards are tightening the encirclement...

Name: Lucia
Text: We have to destroy them all to prevent them from attacking the rescue aircraft.

Name: Bianca
Text: The royal guards are very difficult to handle. If we don't want to be attacked from both sides, we'd better concentrate our firepower on one side first.

Name: Karenina
Text: Commandant, quick! Which side! I'm gonna blow them all to smithereens!

Name: Lucia
Text: Nithart... she turned off the external sensorium of her frame.

Name: Lee
Text: She and the royal guards have already fused into one. Even if we concentrate our firepower on her, we'll still be unable to interrupt the guards' attack.

Name: Karenina
Text: Just blow 'em all up!

Name: Nanami
Text: Can we attack now? Nanami wants to fight!

Name: Bianca
Text: The Golden Vortex will turn into an inferno soon. We'd better go now. We can't let Nithart be on our way...

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant, let's make a clean break with Nithart.

Name: Lee
Text: It's about time.

Name: Kuroro
Text: Ku?

Name: Lee
Text: We can't keep Commandant and Liv waiting.

Name: Kuroro
Text: Kukukuku!

Name: Lee
Text: Phew... Okay, that should be enough.

Name: Kuroro
Text: Kukukukukukukuuu...

Name: Lee
Text: ...Merry Christmas to you all as well.

Name: Elite Corrupted
Text: Urgh—Uuurgh!

Name: Corrupted
Text: Urgh!

Name: Nanami
Text: Whoa, so many bad boys here. Nanami is a good girl who refuses to resort to brute force!

Name: Nanami
Text: Then I should cut more trees quietly without being noticed by them!

Name: Nanami
Text: Yeah! Go!

Name: Nanami
Text: Hm, it looks good, and is far from the Corrupted.

Name: Nanami
Text: Even if I emit some noises, they won't notice when they're cutting trees, right?

Name: Nanami
Text: Okay! Start!

Name: Nanami
Text: These guys... They're just cutting at nothing now, but still aren't stopping...

Name: Nanami
Text: It's getting boring. Nanami's bringing the Christmas tree back! Bye bye!

Name: Nanami
Text: <size=30><color=#ff0000>1!</color></size>

Name: Nanami
Text: <size=50><color=#ff0000>2!</color></size>

Name: Nanami
Text: <size=50>3!</size>

Name: Nanami
Text: <size=70><color=#ffff00>Go!</color></size>

Name: Nanami
Text: <size=80><color=#ff0000>Stop!</color></size>

Name: Karenina
Text: The door blocks our way.

Name: Karenina
Text: What a nuisance. Just bomb 'em with the bugs!

Name: Karenina
Text: Lucia came up with the plan anyway, so she should be the one who has to take care of the consequences.

Name: Karenina
Text: I'll ring the bell before those boomboxes arrive.

Name: Karenina
Text: Hold on, the bell is so rotten that even a single touch will ruin it!

Name: Karenina
Text: Well, I don't care. At least the firework can start on time.

Name: Kamui
Text: The Gray Raven folks are so cold. They're all celebrating Christmas together without inviting me!

Name: Kamui
Text: I even prepared some gifts for them! Since I'm not invited...

Name: Kamui
Text: Let me sneak in from the roof to surprise them...

Name: Kamui
Text: Hm? What are those Corrupted doing? Do they also celebrate Christmas?

Name: Kuroro
Text: Kuku... Kuuu...

Name: Corrupted
Text: Uuuurgh—

Name: Kamui
Text: Kuroro? How did you become so tiny?

Name: Kamui
Text: Wow, you guys are picking on the weak!

Name: Kamui
Text: Don't be afraid! I'm coming to rescue you!

Name: Kamui
Text: Alright, all Corrupted were gone. Are you okay, buddy?

Name: Kuroro
Text: Kuku—ku? Kuku, kuku!!

Name: Kamui
Text: Hm? No need to thank me! It was nothing, hahaha!

Name: Kamui
Text: This is—a Santa Claus costume. Are you going to give it to me as a thank-you gift?

Name: Kuroro
Text: Ku?

Name: Kamui
Text: Great! That's exactly what I want!

Name: Kuroro
Text: Kukuku?

Name: Kamui
Text: You should leave too, so that you don't get bullied by the Corrupted again, buddy!

Name: Kuroro
Text: Ku? Ku? Ku? Ku? Ku?

Name: Kamui
Text: Thanks! Merry Christmas! Bye—

Name: α
Text: Is this one of those... shrines? Where humans used to worship gods in the Golden Age.

Name: α
Text: Do I really have to wear this...?

Name: α
Text: ...Whatever, if Luna wants to see this outfit.

Name: α
Text: There are no gods in this world. Even if there are, they can't save me.

Name: α
Text: But... What if...
(Rustling noises)

Name: α
Text: Tsk, how annoying!

Name: α
Text: ...Gods, if you do exist.

Name: α
Text: Please, make sure Luna is safe.

Name: α
Text: ...Even if gods can't do it, I will make it happen.

Name: α
Text: Better keep going. Luna's waiting for me.

Name: α
Text: Almost there.

Name: α
Text: —I only need to get rid of these trash first.

Name: α
Text: Okay. I should be able to make it on time.

Name: α
Text: ...Wait for me. I will be there for you, right in the first minute of the new year.

Name: Liv
Text: Phew... Only two areas of combat test mission left to go.

Name: Liv
Text: It was Miss Ayla's request to test the New Year Coating's combat adaptability...

Name: Liv
Text: But this is still too...

Name: Liv
Text: No, I must stop thinking. Liv, finish your mission first!

Name: Liv
Text: Miss Ayla is so good... She is not hindered by the outfit at all.

Name: Liv
Text: I wish I can wear this and go to a shrine with everyone of Gray Raven...

Name: Liv
Text: Alright, one final mission left.

Name: Liv
Text: Let's begin!

Name: Liv
Text: Oops, it's almost 12am!

Name: Liv
Text: I'm not in the shrine... But...

Name: Liv
Text: Dear God, I wish all the members of Gray Raven will always be together.

Name: Liv
Text: I hope Commandant can stay safe...

Name: Liv
Text: Thank you, God.

Name: Liv
Text: Alright, time to go back. Commandant and others are waiting for me.

Name: Lucia
Text: Let's go, Commandant.

Name: Lucia
Text: Commandant, that Corrupted that has been acting as a leader is about to run off. Let's go after it.

Name: Lucia
Text: Save your breath. Commandant and I won't spare any single one of Corrupted.

Name: Lucia
Text: Still late... Tch!

Name: Lucia
Text: ...Something has exposed my location for sure.

Name: Lucia
Text: Never mind, I was just talking to myself.

Name: Sophia
Text: I didn't know consciousness connection would be that different from usual.

Name: Lee
Text: I'm like Commandant's little doll. Please take good care of us, will you?

Name: Sophia
Text: Wait... In this sense...

Name: Lee
Text: It seems that the connection between Commandant and here is over. We'll search this area shortly.

Name: Sophia
Text: I'll give it my all, Commandant!

Name: Ayla
Text: Speaking of which, Commandant, have you noticed that some of our voice messages weren't censored?

Name: Ayla
Text: Perhaps it can be used to recognize our true identities.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Will recognizing who we are... really help us get through this situation?

Name: Ayla
Text: Commandant, it seems you have to change your connection target.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Will the next guy find Commandant?

Name: Ayla
Text: Not sure, but we've already narrowed down the range of searching area. We should be able to calculate Commandant's location very soon.

Name: Ayla
Text: I'll see you at that place, Commandant.

Name: Liv
Text: Consciousness connection...

Name: Liv
Text: In a nutshell, Commandant exists within my body in addition to ■■■■■, right?

Name: Liv
Text: Let us show you the power of the trio, Corrupted!

Name: Liv
Text: Ah, It's the message from ■■■■■. I'll go to the rendezvous point too.

Name: Liv
Text: Commandant, wait for me!

Name: Vera
Text: I'll repeat the rules, just for you.

Name: Vera
Text: Those standing before you are the Constructs closest to you.

Name: Vera
Text: The reason they become like this is because of your cognitive bias.

Name: Vera
Text: Next, I'll ask questions like which one is the real Liv and which one is the real Kamui.

Name: Vera
Text: What you need to do is to point out their true identities.

Name: Vera
Text: Of course, it'd be great if you're right. But if you're wrong—

Name: Vera
Text: Nozzle comes close to initiating a self-destruct sequence. This will damage you and the Constructs.

Name: Vera
Text: Humph, are you really be able to recognize each of them? I look forward to your performance.

Name: Vera
Text: What? This is...!

Name: Vera
Text: Wrong. That's a pity. Your Constructs will get hurt if you don't pay more attention.

Name: Vera
Text: First Question. Which one is Kamui?

Name: Vera
Text: Correct, though it's merely a simple one.

Name: Vera
Text: Second question. Which one is Liv?

Name: Vera
Text: Correct. As expected, that humility has made it too obvious.

Name: Vera
Text: Third question. Which one is Bianca?

Name: Vera
Text: How does it feel like to be mistaken for Watanabe, your sworn enemy?

Name: Vera
Text: No need to overreact. I've been watching it from the very beginning.

Name: Vera
Text: Fourth question. Which one is Ayla?

Name: Vera
Text: No fun. When she said association, the answer nearly came to the surface.

Name: Vera
Text: Fifth question. Which one is Chrome?

Name: Vera
Text: That said, Chrome appearing in this place really surprised me. I thought he was preparing for the next special mission.

Name: Vera
Text: Sixth Question. Which one is Lee?

Name: Vera
Text: Well, as you've excluded all deceptive answers, it's no surprise that you chose the correct one.

Name: Vera
Text: Why don't you give scythes a shot? You seem to be a great scythe wielder.

Name: Vera
Text: After all, nothing is hard for you... Hah.

Name: Vera
Text: Seventh question. Which one is Karenina... To be honest, I don't want to go on like this either. The rest are all super simple ones.

Name: Vera
Text: Uh... Alright alright. Correct. All words coming from this mouth would be censored by the connection system.

Name: Vera
Text: The last question. Which one is Lucia? Press the confirm button <color=#ff6633>now</color> to finish this game.

Name: Vera
Text: Why don't you act? Lucia stood right there. You didn't fall asleep, did you?

Name: Vera
Text: ...What!?

Name: Vera
Text: That's not Lucia... Hahahaha, so you really can recognize her. Hahaha!

Name: Vera
Text: Perfect. You're right...

Name: Vera
Text: ...For hell's sake. I knew it. The bond between commandant and Construct is but a joke.

Name: Vera
Text: How can you not recognize the Construct staying by your side all the time?

Name: Vera
Text: No way. How can you pick this one? You're not a moron, aren't you?

Name: Vera
Text: Fine...

Name: Vera
Text: Lu... Musashi, catch that Nozzle!
Here, Commandant!

Name: Watanabe
Text: Hey, Akdilek girl, what are you doing...?

Name: Sophia
Text: Sorry, my hand slipped.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Causing troubles instead of killing me, huh... Lucky that you're a Support type.

Name: Sophia
Text: Sophia doesn't understand what you are talking about.

Name: Watanabe
Text: Whatever... Keep pretending.

Name: Watanabe
Text: But you can't keep hiding. We have big guys coming.

Name: Sophia
Text: As expected, they are Attacker Constructs. Very old models though.

Name: Watanabe
Text: What exactly are you planning?

Name: Lucia
Text: Can I use these leaves?

Name: Watanabe
Text: Yeah, they still have a bitter taste, but I guess we don't have a better option.

Name: Watanabe
Text: We need more though. These aren't enough.

Name: Lee
Text: Corrupted spotted. Let's get rid of them first.

Name: Lucia
Text: I never knew there were plants in the desert.

Name: Liv
Text: I feel sorry for these plants...

Name: Lee
Text: I bet these leaves have never thought they would get picked in a desert.

Name: Lucia
Text: I wonder what kind of zongzi Lucia would like?

Name: Liv
Text: Commandant, I think red bean will be a great addition to the zongzi.

Name: Lee
Text: The leaves are a bit annoying, but zongzi contain meat and rice, making them a great food.

Name: Changyu
Text: This Corrupted... I knew it...

Name: Watanabe
Text: Focus on the Corrupted around you. You could easily die if you get distracted.

Name: Changyu
Text: Yes! Got it.

Name: System Voice
Text: Truth or dare!

Name: System Voice
Text: Answer the other person's question within the time limit!

Name: System Voice
Text: If you can't answer, or refuse to... You'll have to perform a daring forfeit!

Name: Liv
Text: So this is like a mind training, where Liv must answer Commandant's questions. I will do my best!

Name: System Voice
Text: Question: What's your fondest wish?

Name: Liv
Text: To defeat Punishing Virus and take back the Earth.

Name: System Voice
Text: Question: What will you do if your most important person argues with you?

Name: Liv
Text: Could it be... I have done something wrong? I'll try to correct my mistake, and apologize to Com—to that person, I mean.

Name: System Voice
Text: Question: Which type of boyfriend do you prefer: cat or dog?

Name: Liv
Text: Huh...? What do you mean by cat and dog...?

Name: Kamui
Text: An animal as boyfriend...?

Name: Lee
Text: No way.

Name: System Voice
Text: Too bad! You failed to answer within the time limit! You must face a forfeit!

Name: Liv
Text: The ammo of my Levi-Gun has all become water... Is it because we are in a game?

Name: Lee
Text: It's a game from the Golden Age. The questions are probably based on the pop culture of that era.

Name: Liv
Text: I see. I need a better understanding of the Golden Age culture to answer these questions.

Name: Liv
Text: Let me connect to the old human database... Alright. Liv will be able to answer any question now!
Here comes the first question—
<color=#ff0000>What is the most horrible thing you have ever done to Commandant?</color>

Name: Liv
Text: What?! How can there be such a question? How did it know...
Countdown: 3—2—

Name: Liv
Text: Argh... I-I once took away the snacks that Commandant hid in the room!
The second question is—
<color=#ff0000>Tell us one thing that you regret the most.</color>

Name: Liv
Text: ...There are many of them. I can't really tell them all...
Hmm... Let's skip this question then.
Last question: <color=#ff0000>Tell us one thing that you absolutely don't want Commandant to know!</color>

Name: Liv
Text: Absolutely...not...

Name: Kamui
Text: Liv, are you alright? Your face looks really red.

Name: Liv
Text: I... I choose the dare!

Name: Nanami
Text: Here—comes—Nanami!

Name: Lee
Text: You just put your personal data in here... That was so risky.

Name: Lee
Text: I trust you have heard us. They are very important, so you must not break them.

Name: Nanami
Text: Nanami found them! Don't stop Nanami!

Name: Watermelon
Text: The watermelon has a metallic shine. This must be the "mission item" that Liv mentioned.

Name: Surfboard
